No. 546,

Misc.

Patterson, Warden, et al. v. Arraj, Chief Judge, U. S. District Court. Duke W. Dunbar, Attorney General of Colorado, and John E. Bush and John P. Moore, Assistant Attorneys General, for petitioners. Michael A. Williams for respondent.

Motion for leave to proceed on mimeographed papers granted. Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus denied.
